\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 Decision Title
\f1\b0 : Offline Mode App Integration \
\'a0\

\f0\b Context
\f1\b0 : Creating an offline mode for customers to browse products and view order history, even if they are not connected to the internet.\

\f0\b \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Options Considered
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Application content can only be viewed when connected to the internet.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Products and order history are accessible to view without the internet.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Support both an online and offline version for browsing retail company products.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Decision
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 The decision is made to limit app access to online use only.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\
\'a0\

\f0\b Rationale
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 In the context of online shopping, product can move quickly, and product availability should be up-to-date to enhance customer experience.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 If a user shops offline, synchronizing with the server when internet access become available may affect performance as it may need to update the app every time it is opened. \
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 If a user shops offline and discovers a product is out-of-stock when internet accessibility is available, it may negatively impact customer experience.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 If a user is trying to access the application offline to track the status of their deliveries, it\'92s unlikely they will receive up-to-date information.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Consequences
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Users will need to have internet access to fully utilize the shopping application.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 App performance may be better off if it does not need to sync data once internet is available.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Less strain on data servers to store offline data.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Follow-Up Actions
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Identify data servers that can deliver product information quickly when internet access is available.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Ensure real-time services like updating inventory, tracking orders, and viewing order history are up-to-date every time the user opens the app. \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
