\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 Decision Title
\f1\b0 : Inclusion of Push Notifications to Notify Customers about Product Updates.\

\f0\b \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Context
\f1\b0 : Having push notifications enabled to inform customers about updates with their orders, the arrival of new products, and exclusive offers.\

\f0\b \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Options Considered
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Designing the application to integrate with existing push notification services to deliver notifications.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Restricting the application from delivering push notifications to users.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Allowing users to opt-in and customize which push notifications they would like to receive.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Decision
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 The decision is made to allow users to opt-in to push notifications and to customize what they want to receive notifications about.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Rationale
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Push notifications are the ideal tool to keep customers informed of up-to-date news and exciting offers.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Customers may also want to know information and updates about the status of their order, or if new products are announced. \
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Allowing customers to opt-in to notifications ensures limitation with advertising fatigue, which may come when apps send out consistent push notifications and causes users to lose interest and engagement with the application. \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Consequences
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 App will need to be integrated with existing push notification systems on the customers desired device OS. \
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 App will need to adjust to any customizations or changes made to the delivery frequency and content of push notifications as specified by the user. \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b \'a0
\f1\b0 \

