\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Designing the app to work alongside existing push notification services that handle the delivery of notifications.\
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Programming application to deliver notifications to users as per their customization choices.\
