\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 Decision Title
\f1\b0 : Integration of Various Payment Gateways for Secure and Convenient Transactions.\
\'a0\

\f0\b Context
\f1\b0 : Integrating access to a secure and convenient payment gateway to ensure ease of use and compatibility with the app\'92s target platform.\
\'a0\

\f0\b Options Considered
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f4\i\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Plaid API
\f1\i0\b0  - a financial technology company that provides APIs that can connect and verify bank accounts, as well as facilitate financial transactions [1]. Plaid uses encryption and data tokenization for their security measures [1].\uc0\u8232 \u8232 \
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f4\i\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 PayPal Payflow \'96 
\f1\i0\b0 a payment gateway service that is straightforward to use, works internationally, and secured with encryption and fraud detection systems [2]. They also offer a buyer protection program which can help resolve any customer disputes and provide refunds in the event of an unauthorized transaction [2].\uc0\u8232 \u8232 \
\uc0\u9679 
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f4\i\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Shopify Payments
\f1\i0\b0  \'96 Shopify Payments is a payment gateway services built directly into the Shopify platform, allowing customers to easily tracks orders and the integration of point-of-sale hardware for both online and in-store retail [3]. Shopify payments use fraud detection software and adhere to PCI DSS standards to reduce potential fraud and security threats [3].\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Decision
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 The decision was made to integrate Plaid API as the payment gateway service for retail company\'92s checkout.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Rationale
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 While all options considered had robust security measures in place to protect a customer\'92s personal and financial information, Plaid was the only service to offer a payment gateway API that easily integrates into the application, \

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 While timelessly credible, the Shopify Payments gateway is only seamlessly integrated for business websites using the Shopify platform. If the retail company chooses to develop their store outside of the Shopify platform, there are no guarantees the Shopify Payments gateway will be compatible. \

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 PayPal Payflow is also very credible as a payment gateway service. However, there are some issues and concerns around transaction fees, as they charge per payment processed. It may be a suitable option for a business with low traffic, but the cost will add up as scalability of the business grows. Additionally, while their buyer protection program offers security and peace of mind to consumers, it may result in a loss of revenue for the merchant if there are numerous disputes that occur.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Consequences
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Using Plaid API as a payment gateway service will allow for more customization as it pertains to the online retailer\'92s website, such as tailoring the experience of the checkout process.\

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Plaid offers APIs and SDKs that allow for easy integration of their services into websites and applications, which may optimize the development process.\

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 However, if a customer holds a bank account that is not supported by Plaid, it may limit the range of consumers they can appeal to. \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\

\f0\b Follow-Up Actions
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Deciding on a Plaid API that integrates well with the retail company\'92s application.\

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Development of a loyalty program for discounts that integrates with the Plaid API. \

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Integration of the Plaid API to allow provide information around tracking orders and viewing order history. \

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Selecting a Plaid API that seamlessly integrates into the app that also processes information about returns and exchanges. \uc0\u8232 \
