\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 Decision Title
\f1\b0 : Display Product Images and Deciding an Image Storage Solution\
\'a0\

\f0\b Context
\f1\b0 : Develop an app that will store images files that correlate to the inventory by images in varying sizes and resolutions. \
\'a0\

\f0\b Options Considered
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Local Storage \'96 
\f1\b0 Hard drives (HDDs) or solid-state drives (SSDs), can offer high read and write speeds, especially when dealing with large datasets or require low latency [8]. This would be ideal for high resolution file types.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \'a0
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Cloud Storage \'96 
\f1\b0 Enables organizations to store, access, and maintain data so that a user is not required to own or operate their own data centres. Cloud storage is scalable, allowing organizations to expand or reduce their data footprint depending on their needs [9].\
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \'a0
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Hybrid Solution \'96 
\f1\b0 By combining private (local) and public (cloud) storage, hybrid storage combines agility and scalability with control and security. It is also the cheaper route over building physical data centres for storage. \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Decision
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 The decision was made to implement a Hybrid solution that combines local caching and cloud storage. \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Rationale
\f1\b0 \
