\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 Decision Title
\f1\b0 : Scalability of Application to Support International Customers\
\'a0\

\f0\b Context
\f1\b0 : Support international customers effectively, the app must be able to handle increased traffic, provide relevant, localized content and maintain optimal performance across different geographic locations.\'a0 \
\'a0\

\f0\b Options Considered
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Multi-CDN (Multiple Content Delivery Network) -
\f1\b0 \'a0 involves using multiple CDN providers at the same time to deliver content. This approach leverages the strengths of various CDNs to enhance performance, reliability and coverage. \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \'a0
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Regional Caching \'96
\f1\b0  placing caches (servers that store copies of frequently accessed data) in specific geographic regions to reduce latency and improve access times for users in those areas. Can be accomplished with a single CDN.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 Hybrid CDN
\f1\b0  \'96 supplements existing content delivery services with private CDN components to boost efficiency and performance [10].\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Decision
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 The decision was made to apply a Hybrid CDN that combines multiple CDNs and regional caching.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Rationale
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-480\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf2 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
