\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Multi CDN allows for centralized management, while regional caching handles local spikes in traffic effectively\

\f5 \'b7
\f2\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 Regional caching provides redundancy that will reduce the potential for failure\
